        <U extends T> javafx.scene.Node configureCell(TreeItemData<U> data,
                                              javafx.scene.Node content)
        Used to change the default cell configuration strategy.

        Here is also a good place to mark a cell with a pseudo-class to flag for custom css styling.

        Type Parameters:
        U - the specific type of the tree item
        Parameters:
        data - the data contents of the tree item
        content - the current cell content for the tree item

        the new cell content for the tree item
